attributes.action: TELL US if the secrecy over the confidante paedophile Patrick Rock is the level of protection that those named in the Dickens dossier can expect.
attributes.additional_details: It appears that ANYBODY who is very close to David Cameron can eventually find themselves before our courts for activity far and beyond the call of duty supporting our corrupt prime minister.  Is there ANYTHING that is beneath Number 10 when it comes to denying the public the information to which they are entitled - HOW THEY ARE, AS A NATION, BEING ABUSED BY THEIR ELECTED DISHONOURABLES.
